    {
        "_id": "65089527b35e73d543766e2e",
        "title": "Great Grace Mission Empowerment Program",
        "slug": "great-grace-mission",
        "heroImage": "650894e3b35e73d543766e25",
        "content": [
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": "GREAT GRACE MISSION EMPOWERMENT PROGRAM"
                    }
                ],
                "type": "h1"
            },
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": " ILARO, OGUN STATE ON SEPTEMBER 9 ,2023"
                    }
                ],
                "type": "h3"
            },
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": "",
                        "code": true
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": ""
                    }
                ],
                "type": "upload",
                "value": {
                    "id": "650896d0b35e73d543766fab"
                },
                "relationTo": "media"
            },
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": ""
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": "Golem Nigeria Outreach in Junction with Great Grace Mission held an empowerment program for widows , orphans and less privileged in the city of Ilaro , Ogun State on September 9, 2023. "
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": ""
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": "It was an event that witnessed the presence of widows, orphans, and the less privileged from different parts of Yewa.\""
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": ""
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": "The event started as soon as the Golem NIgeria Outreach team arrived  at 11:50 am  with an opening prayer from the church  leader followed by praises and thanksgiving lead by the Great Grace Mission team."
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": ""
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": "Later , a short  history of Great Grace Mission was briefed by Pastor Asamu followed by a short address from the Director of Golem Nigeria , Deacon Tunde Bamidele."
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": ""
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": "The presentation of writing materials to school pupils was done afterwards and then the meal items were shared to the widows accordingly. "
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": ""
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": "The occasion came to an end with  a vote of thanks from on of the widows and then a closing prayer by one of the church pastors. "
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": ""
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": "The program came to a halt at 1:45 pm. "
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": ""
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": ""
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "children": [
                    {
                        "text": " Public Affairs",
                        "bold": true
                    }
                ]
            }
        ],
